description: The Real Estate Select Sector SPDR Fund seeks to provide investment results that, before expenses, correspond generally to the price and yield performance of the Real Estate Select Sector Index (the “Index”)The Index seeks to provide an effective representation of the real estate sector of the S&P 500 IndexSeeks to provide precise exposure to companies from real estate management and development and REITs, excluding mortgage REITsAllows investors to take strategic or tactical positions at a more targeted level than traditional style based investing
name: The Real Estate Select Sector SPDR Fund
